# Claude Code project artifacts — override global ~/.gitignore_global which excludes .claude/
# Tracked: project-shared slash commands, scripts, hook configuration.
# Untracked: .claude/launch.json (per-machine preferences) and anything else not explicitly listed.
!.claude/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/commands/fact-check-review.md
!.claude/scripts/
!.claude/scripts/auto-deploy.sh
!.claude/scripts/fact-check-checklist.txt
!.claude/settings.json
